quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  19,16,"Nabiyow ama Qhuraan kitaabih addal Maryam xaagu cusey, is isi marak texxeereeh, keenik ayro mawqat raaqa aracal gacte waqdi"
  19,17,"Tokkel is isi maraa kee isi fanat tet qellisa reebu haysitte Qibaada abta wagqdi tet able waanamkeh, tokkel jibriil deqsita ni malaykattu tet fanah rubneeh gino kak dudda-le seehadaytih weelot weeloysimmi iyyeh teetih yemeete"
  19,18,"Maryam diggah anu Racmaan kinni Rabbi kok maggansitak, Yallak meesita num tekkek umaaneh gabah yoo maxagin kaak itte"
  19,19,"Cagalah anu ku-Rabbih farmoyta kinniyooh, usuk koo fan yoo ruube, dambittek saytunnoowe awka koh aceemkeh teetik iyye jibriil"
  19,20,Maryam jibriilik awka xalaah geyam mannal yoh takkee rihimih seehadayti yoo mabtinnaay yol kalah yol xayyowtem matanaay anu timixxige dalweynah masuginniyyok? kaak itte
  19,21,"Jibriil Maryamak: caagid atu kah itta inna kinnih immay, ku-Rabbi abba sinni baxa ginaah koh aceem yol xabcinih iyye, kaadu sinaamah Yallih dudda elle yaaxigen asta kaa abne kaal yeemeneeh kaa kataate marah nek yan Racmatah, kaaduNabii Qiisâ gino yookome caagidiy meklimey lowcal macfuuzul yunkuttube kinni"
  19,22,"Tokkel jibriil maryamak diriqik (korta kinnuk) moyya kak culta ikkek ufuy fuufuseeh, too fufto maxaxa teetik toofeeh tohih sabbatah Qiisal tussukuqqeeh, tokkel kaa bagut luk Sinaamak texxeereeh xer aracal gacte"
  19,23,"Tokkel lacaw tamirtô laqibih fan tet beeh tet kelse kaa tabbixemkeh, is lacaw Qansarih gibdah: maganey ahak duma rabeh suginniyoy, kaadu sinam burah cabteemiy xagar kak xage waytaah kassite waytah suginniyoy yoh aysuk ten itte"
  19,24,"Tokkel jibriil tamirtô gubak teetih seece: maryamey marookitin. Nummah ku-Rabbi qunxa weeqaytu (qunxa dara kinnuk) gubat kok heek iyyaanamah"
  19,25,Kaadu tamirtô laqib isi fan esgeyyi hayis alee tamiray batayah yaniy woo waqdi daggiime kol caxelek (luuquse-lek)
  19,26,"Toysa atu ama tamiray batayah yanik akumaay, ama qunxa weeqaytih leek aqubaay ama baxat inti wagrisaay ruffu kaat ixxic; tokkel sinaamak numuk teyna tubleeh, tokkel usuk atu xalte baxih xaagu kok abek, toysa diggah anu racmaan kinni rabbih tibbi axcem axbuuxuh innil hee kaak ixxic, (nadri kinnuk) asaaku inkinnah seehadaytu luk yaabe waamah"
  19,27,"Maryam xer ikkek isi baxa quukak isi maral temeete, usun tet kee tet baxa yublen waqdi : Maryamey nummah kaxxaamay umay assocokkile bahte teetik iyyen"
  19,28,Haaruun toobokoytáy (maqanxay) kabba uma numuy dalweynah yanih masuginnaay ku ina dalweynay dalwa abtah masuginnak; a-baxa ankek litoo teetik iyyen
  19,29,"Tokkel maryam isi baxa Qiisâ fanah escessi hayte kaa esseraanamkeh, tet yab qajibsitak: saldih yan awkay handuulut yanî luk mannal yabnaah teetik iyyen"
  19,30,"Nabii Qiisa handuulut (sarô lollo kinnuk) anuk: diggah anu Yallih naqsuuy Yalli injiil deqsita kitab yoh yeceeh isi Nabii yoo abe keenik iyye"
  19,31,"Kaadu yi Rabbi kayrii kee tuxxiq kak maggo num yoo abe elle aninnaan rikel, kaadu usuk salat abaah dacrisaah zaka aceemih yoo farriime nuwwiyom fanah"
  19,32,"Kaadu inni inah amqeeh tet amri oggola num yoo abe, kaadu kaxxamariinoley daalimtuh yaniy isi Rabbih amri cina yoo maabinna keenik iyye"
  19,33,"Kaadu ooboke ayrooy, raba ayroo kee nuwwuk ugutuwaa ayro (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk) Yallak nagaynan yol yanay"
  19,34,Nabii Mucammadow woo Maryam baxa Nabii Qiisâ weeloo kee xaaguy kol maaqne nummâ cakki maxcoy yahuud kee nasaara edde agaywaagitta kinni
  19,35,"Yalli isi ginok baxa haaysitam kaa macelta usuk wohuk saytunnooweh ikkal, cagalah usuk caagiidak caagidik teyna meklam faxa waqdi tik iyyaah wohim xayih usuk elle faxa innal takke"
  19,36,"Nabii Qiisa isi marak: diggah Yallay sin fan kak seeca usuk yi- Rabbiiy sin Rabbik, toysa dibuk kaa uqbuda usuk agleyta malik, tamah massa-le gitay mako sinni kinnik keenik iyye"
  19,37,"Kitab marak buttaati Qiisâ caagidil itta wayteh ittin fanal, tokkel koroosite marah finqi yan Qhiyaamah ayroy kaxxam gibdiy meesi le yabloonu waana"
  19,38,"Oobbaa kee mabul manxu keenik (koros kinnuk) gibdii Qhiyaamah ayroy cisab kee galtoh nee fan yamaatoonu waana, kinnih immay korosuy daalimiinih tani ta-asaaku addunyal cakkik baxxaqqa-le makoh addat tan"
  19,39,"Nabiyow ken meesis nadaamah ayroy (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk) caagid meklimay ginô fan baxsaanaah moominiiniy jannat cultaa kee korosuy gira culta yakken waqdi, usun (koros kinnuk) asaaku addunyal ken kak meesiiseenimik garcit anuk usun rabak lakal ugut yaniih mano tanim manummaysan"
  19,40,Diggah Nanu baaxoo kee baaxô bagul tanim inkih nanu nagarraah usun cisab kee galtoh nee fan gacsiman